                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                        3. Medical Disclaimer
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        The information on this site is not a substitute for
                        professional medical advice. Always consult your doctor
                        before starting any treatment or remedy.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">4. User Conduct</h2>
                    <p>
                        You agree not to misuse the site or engage in any
                        activity that disrupts its functionality or violates
                        laws.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                        5. External Links
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        Our website may contain links to third-party websites.
                        AyurCure Daily is not responsible for the content or
                        practices of those websites.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">
                        6. Changes to Terms
                    </h2>
                    <p>
                        We may update these Terms & Conditions from time to
                        time. Continued use of the site means you accept any
                        changes made.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
                    <p>
                        For any questions or concerns regarding these terms,
                        please contact us at <a
                            href="mailto: ayurcuredaily@gmail.com"
                            class="text-primary-600 underline"
                            >ayurcuredaily@gmail.com</a
                        >.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
